metadata.description: D8A DAO is created by gamers, developers, and entertainers with the vision of building a blended experience powered by Web 3.0, Unreal 5, and cutting edge architecture. The primary purpose of this community is to generate meaningful social engagements while supporting creatives globally in a joint effort to reimagine entertainment. The Emerald Key offers a low barrier to entry to the DAO along with its own unique Value. There are 42000 keys initially that can be burned and upgraded at any time to either Silver or Gold Keys. Emerald Keys have a decreasing supply and can be traded after a 90 Day Lock period.
metadata.name: Emerald Key
